
# newer technologies
    > Inversion of Control
    > AOP

# Without EJB
    > EJB is heavy and in many cases it is a problem in itself

    J2EE(Java2 Platform Enterprise Edition) is more than EJB.Using J2EE without EJB, we don't have to reinvent the wheel.
    We don't need to reimplement J2EE services, just consider alternative ways of tapping into them.

# Themes
    The central themes:
    > The primacy of business requirements
    > Simplicity
    > Productivity
    > The fundamental importance of object orientation

# Pareto Principle
    a small number of cause(10%-20%) are responsible for most(80%-90%) of the effect.We just emphasize the common
    problems.

    EJB试图解决所有复杂问题，从而把自己搞得很复杂。在实际的工作中，80%-90%都是简单而Happy的coding工作，但就是由于EJB的复杂而导致解决
    简单问题的时候也要按照复杂问题的套路：效率太低了。

    连喜欢装B的人都不会用EJB。
